"{\"value\":{\"mdx\":\"# Payment and Billing\\n\\n## Set Up Your Account Balance\\n\\nTo use model services, you need to top up your escrow account with tokens:\\n\\n### Using the CLI\\n\\n1. **Get the Service Token**: Contact your AiMo Network node operator for the token mint address\\n2. **Top Up Your Escrow**: You'll need to deposit tokens into your escrow account managed by the router\\n\\n### Using the Dashboard\\n\\nYou can also top up your account balance directly through our web dashboard, which provides a user-friendly interface for account management.\\n\\nThe escrow system ensures secure, automated payments for model usage without requiring manual approval for each request.\\n\\n## How Payments Work\\n\\n1. **Escrow Account**: Your tokens are held in a secure escrow account\\n2. **Pre-Authorization**: Before each request, the system estimates and locks the maximum cost\\n3. **Actual Settlement**: After the request completes, you're charged only for actual usage\\n4. **Automatic Recovery**: If a request fails, locked tokens are automatically recovered\\n\\n## Usage Tracking\\n\\nPayments are calculated based on:\\n\\n- **Token Usage**: Input tokens (prompt) and output tokens (completion)\\n- **Provider Pricing**: Each provider sets their own pricing per token\\n- **Model Type**: Different models may have different pricing\\n\\n## Managing Your Balance\\n\\n- **Check Balance**: Monitor your escrow balance through your wallet or node operator tools\\n- **Top Up**: Add more tokens to your escrow account when needed\\n- **Withdraw**: Unused tokens can be withdrawn from your escrow account\\n\",\"document\":[{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#payment-and-billing\",\"html\":\"</header>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#payment-and-billing\",\"isPage\":true,\"text\":\"\\n\",\"title\":\"Payment and Billing\",\"titles\":[]},{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#set-up-your-account-balance\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>To use model services, you need to top up your escrow account with tokens:</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#set-up-your-account-balance\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nTo use model services, you need to top up your escrow account with tokens:\\n\",\"title\":\"Set Up Your Account Balance\",\"titles\":[\"Payment and Billing\"]},{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#using-the-cli\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li><strong>Get the Service Token</strong>: Contact your AiMo Network node operator for the token mint address</li>\\n<li><strong>Top Up Your Escrow</strong>: You&#x27;ll need to deposit tokens into your escrow account managed by the router</li>\\n</ol>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#using-the-cli\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nGet the Service Token: Contact your AiMo Network node operator for the token mint address\\nTop Up Your Escrow: You&#x27;ll need to deposit tokens into your escrow account managed by the router\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Using the CLI\",\"titles\":[\"Payment and Billing\",\"Set Up Your Account Balance\"]},{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#using-the-dashboard\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>You can also top up your account balance directly through our web dashboard, which provides a user-friendly interface for account management.</p>\\n<p>The escrow system ensures secure, automated payments for model usage without requiring manual approval for each request.</p>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#using-the-dashboard\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nYou can also top up your account balance directly through our web dashboard, which provides a user-friendly interface for account management.\\nThe escrow system ensures secure, automated payments for model usage without requiring manual approval for each request.\\n\",\"title\":\"Using the Dashboard\",\"titles\":[\"Payment and Billing\",\"Set Up Your Account Balance\"]},{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#how-payments-work\",\"html\":\"\\n<ol>\\n<li><strong>Escrow Account</strong>: Your tokens are held in a secure escrow account</li>\\n<li><strong>Pre-Authorization</strong>: Before each request, the system estimates and locks the maximum cost</li>\\n<li><strong>Actual Settlement</strong>: After the request completes, you&#x27;re charged only for actual usage</li>\\n<li><strong>Automatic Recovery</strong>: If a request fails, locked tokens are automatically recovered</li>\\n</ol>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#how-payments-work\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nEscrow Account: Your tokens are held in a secure escrow account\\nPre-Authorization: Before each request, the system estimates and locks the maximum cost\\nActual Settlement: After the request completes, you&#x27;re charged only for actual usage\\nAutomatic Recovery: If a request fails, locked tokens are automatically recovered\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"How Payments Work\",\"titles\":[\"Payment and Billing\"]},{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#usage-tracking\",\"html\":\"\\n<p>Payments are calculated based on:</p>\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Token Usage</strong>: Input tokens (prompt) and output tokens (completion)</li>\\n<li><strong>Provider Pricing</strong>: Each provider sets their own pricing per token</li>\\n<li><strong>Model Type</strong>: Different models may have different pricing</li>\\n</ul>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#usage-tracking\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nPayments are calculated based on:\\n\\nToken Usage: Input tokens (prompt) and output tokens (completion)\\nProvider Pricing: Each provider sets their own pricing per token\\nModel Type: Different models may have different pricing\\n\\n\",\"title\":\"Usage Tracking\",\"titles\":[\"Payment and Billing\"]},{\"href\":\"/user-guide/payments#managing-your-balance\",\"html\":\"\\n<ul>\\n<li><strong>Check Balance</strong>: Monitor your escrow balance through your wallet or node operator tools</li>\\n<li><strong>Top Up</strong>: Add more tokens to your escrow account when needed</li>\\n<li><strong>Withdraw</strong>: Unused tokens can be withdrawn from your escrow account</li>\\n</ul>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/user-guide/payments.mdx#managing-your-balance\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\n\\nCheck Balance: Monitor your escrow balance through your wallet or node operator tools\\nTop Up: Add more tokens to your escrow account when needed\\nWithdraw: Unused tokens can be withdrawn from your escrow account\\n\",\"title\":\"Managing Your Balance\",\"titles\":[\"Payment and Billing\"]}]}}"
